      "comment": "STAR TESTYMONY (1) is a former Victorian who has had three runs for the new yard and is fitter for two runs back. The latest was running on hard to finish runner-up in the Derby Cup, beating a host of others engaged on today's card. Looks ready to win and gets chance. FORTUNE'S LUCK (4) raced on speed and was poor in the Derby Cup but the starts prior led and gave a sight here. Low draw and will take running down. SCHUHBECK (8) has been safely held last couple and is having first try at the trip. Light weight and can give a sight. STREET MASCHINO (7) is suited by the longer trip and can make amends. ALOTTA DANE (3) is ready to peak after two runs back and cannot be discounted.",
